<b>MERC-88</b> will serve as the portable basic ML Agent stack for specialized, reasoning retrieval tools which can operate in small to medium scale business and home environments. 

<h5>Roadmap to 0.1</h5>
*refine python module list
*define current scope
*clear prompts for user variables, set before running retrieval or file handling operations
*files should be formatted on the fly, (ebook, plaintext, pdf)
